<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:13:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>埃克森美孚领导的圭亚那石油集团 2023 年净值跃升，利润率超过英伟达</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-led-guyana-oil-groups-net-jumps-2023-margins-top-nvidias-2024-06-25/</link><description>政府数据显示，圭亚那去年与埃克森美孚领导的南美国家财团达成的利润丰厚的协议为合作伙伴带来了 63.3 亿美元的收入，净利润率高于芯片制造商英伟达公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 09:05:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/exxon-led-guyana-oil-groups-net-jumps-2023-margins-top-nvidias-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促欧盟撤销对中国企业与俄罗斯联系的制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-urges-eu-revoke-sanctions-chinese-firms-over-russian-links-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国周二敦促欧盟撤销对其认为支持俄罗斯乌克兰战争的中国公司的制裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 08:06:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-urges-eu-revoke-sanctions-chinese-firms-over-russian-links-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国开发商世茂在清算听证会前提高了债务重组条款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-developer-shimao-sweetens-debt-revamp-terms-ahead-liquidation-hearing-2024-06-25/</link><description>三名消息人士称，世茂集团已经优化了其离岸债务重组条款，以赢得债权人的支持，这家中国房地产开发商正忙于抵御向香港法院提起的清算申请。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:32:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinese-developer-shimao-sweetens-debt-revamp-terms-ahead-liquidation-hearing-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>诺和诺德减肥药Wegovy在中国获批</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-says-semaglutide-approved-long-term-weight-management-china-2024-06-25/</link><description>诺和诺德周二表示，其广受欢迎的减肥药Wegovy已在中国获得批准，为在全球第二大经济体的销售铺平了道路。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:19:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/novo-nordisk-says-semaglutide-approved-long-term-weight-management-china-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国嫦娥六号月球探测器返回地球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-change-6-moon-probe-lands-back-earth-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国嫦娥六号月球探测器周二在内蒙古北部地区着陆，使中国成为第一个从月球背面带回样本的国家。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:19:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-change-6-moon-probe-lands-back-earth-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>战后数十年，朝鲜仍在修建边界并鸣枪警告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/decades-after-war-north-korea-still-builds-borders-draws-warning-shots-2024-06-25/</link><description>朝鲜战争爆发 74 年后，朝鲜军队正在修建新的防御工事，偶尔会招致韩国军队越过一直处于战争状态的边境线发出警告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 05:25:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/decades-after-war-north-korea-still-builds-borders-draws-warning-shots-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>47名香港民主党人的里程碑式审判进入宣判前的最后阶段</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landmark-trial-47-hong-kong-democrats-enters-final-stretch-before-sentencing-2024-06-25/</link><description>香港有史以来规模最大的针对香港民主反对派的国家安全审判的减刑请求于周二启动，预计这是宣判前的最后阶段，部分被告可能被判处终身监禁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 04:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/landmark-trial-47-hong-kong-democrats-enters-final-stretch-before-sentencing-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国反击西方电动汽车、锂电池产能过剩指控</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-its-evs-lithium-batteries-meet-domestic-demand-enrich-global-supply-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国总理李强在大连举行的世界经济论坛会议上发表讲话，回击了美国和欧盟的指控，即中国企业从不公平补贴中受益，并准备用廉价的绿色技术涌入其市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-its-evs-lithium-batteries-meet-domestic-demand-enrich-global-supply-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾表示希望与中国合作应对南海紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-wants-talk-with-china-south-china-sea-foreign-minister-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>马尼拉外交部长周二表示，上周发生导致一名菲律宾水手严重受伤的冲突后，菲律宾致力于与中国合作制定“建立信任措施”，以应对南海紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 03:47:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-wants-talk-with-china-south-china-sea-foreign-minister-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达暴跌冲击科技板块，欧洲股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-25/</link><description>周一，芯片制造商英伟达股价下跌 7%，拖累美国科技公司，欧洲股市周二下跌，表明人们对人工智能热潮感到紧张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 02:28:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在日本推出第三款电动汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-launches-third-ev-model-japan-2024-06-25/</link><description>中国比亚迪周二表示，在日本推出了第三款电动汽车，这款轿车将是该公司迄今为止在日本市场上最昂贵的车型，而消费者长期以来一直青睐国产品牌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 02:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-launches-third-ev-model-japan-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>美元因日本干预威胁而下跌，日元脆弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-flirts-with-key-160-yen-level-intervention-risk-looms-2024-06-25/</link><description>周二，美元试图突破160日元关键水平，但收效甚微，因为担心日本官员干预，交易员不敢对日元兑其他货币进行过于严厉的惩罚。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:52:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-flirts-with-key-160-yen-level-intervention-risk-looms-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>油价稳定，美国消费者价格数据成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-markets-weigh-supply-tensions-china-economic-recovery-2024-06-25/</link><description>受今年夏季燃料需求增加的预期推动，油价在前一交易日上涨后，周二几乎没有变化，但投资者在美国消费者价格数据公布之前持谨慎态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:44:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-prices-steady-markets-weigh-supply-tensions-china-economic-recovery-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：美国调查中国电信、中国移动互联网、云风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-probing-china-telecom-china-mobile-over-internet-cloud-risks-2024-06-25/</link><description>三名知情人士称，拜登政府正在调查中国移动、中国电信和中国联通，因为担心这些公司可能通过其美国云和互联网业务向北京提供美国数据。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 00:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/us-probing-china-telecom-china-mobile-over-internet-cloud-risks-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>普华永道表示，随着员工拥抱人工智能、提高技能，“伟大的辞职”进入第三个年头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/great-resignation-enters-third-year-workers-embrace-ai-upskilling-pwc-says-2024-06-24/</link><description>普华永道对全球劳动力的一项调查发现，预计在未来 12 个月内更换雇主的工人比例高于 2022 年“大辞职”时期的比例。</description><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 23:07:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/great-resignation-enters-third-year-workers-embrace-ai-upskilling-pwc-says-2024-06-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>